11) Konjunktionen (bağlaçlar)

# SUBORDINATING CONJ.
weil - because
damit - so that
seitdem - since then
soweit - as far as
wohin - where to
wie viel - how much
ob - if, whether
obwohl - although
als ob - as if
als wenn - as when
bis - until
indem - in which
sobald - as soon as
sooft - as often as
wie lange - how long
wie oft - how often
nachdem - after which
solange - as long as
soviel - as much as
warum - why
woher - where from
weshalb - why/for what reason




